```

but **you need to copy the files to the windows machine in order to execute it**, for me this is **/mnt/c/Users/joschie/**.

### verbose build

``` diff
diff --git a/package.nix b/package.nix
index c9e50c399..0f8c5711e 100644
--- a/package.nix
+++ b/package.nix
@@ -313,6 +313,8 @@ in {
